Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.79,0:01:47.42,Main,Thunder Soldier,0,0,0,,Agora vamos pegar o túnel subterrâneo...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.42,0:01:49.02,Main,Thunder Soldier,0,0,0,,...e vamos ao porto comercial inimigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.02,0:01:52.62,Main,Leo,0,0,0,,Nosso objetivo é uma garota,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.84,0:01:55.43,Main,Leo,0,0,0,,Sugar!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.43,0:01:58.41,Main,Flapper,0,0,0,,Mesmo que seja uma garota, \Nnão podemos subestimá-la!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.41,0:02:03.54,Main,Leo,0,0,0,,Vamos acabar com Sugar e fazer com que todos os brinquedos do país voltem a ser humanos!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.66,0:02:15.25,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,É muito estreito!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.25,0:02:18.45,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Robiland e eu mal conseguiríamos passar.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.45,0:02:23.59,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Fraland, é melhor você tirar seus braços e ombros.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.59,0:02:24.76,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Não posso fazer isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.78,0:02:29.90,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Ei, esse túnel é muito\N pequeno para mim.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.90,0:02:35.05,Main,Leo,0,0,0,,Não esperávamos que pessoas grandes o usassem.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.05,0:02:37.00,Main,Thunder Soldier,0,0,0,,Você terá que entrar pela Casa dos Brinquedos.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.52,0:02:41.87,Main,Thunder Soldier,0,0,0,,A Casa dos Brinquedos fica abaixo do planalto do palácio real.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.87,0:02:46.07,Main,Thunder Soldier,0,0,0,,É para onde os brinquedos vão todas as noites.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.07,0:02:48.08,Main,Thunder Soldier,0,0,0,,Humanos não podem entrar.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.08,0:02:51.65,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Casa? É lá que os brinquedos vivem?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.65,0:02:53.96,Main,Thunder Soldier,0,0,0,,É uma casa só de nome.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.96,0:02:56.59,Main,Thunder Soldier,0,0,0,,Não tem camas nem nada.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.59,0:03:00.43,Main,Thunder Soldier,0,0,0,,Só tem um passagem subterrânea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.43,0:03:04.73,Main,Thunder Soldier,0,0,0,,Noite após noite, os brinquedos usam essa passagem...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.73,0:03:07.04,Main,Thunder Soldier,0,0,0,,...e trabalham no subsolo a noite toda.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.96,0:03:13.10,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Então, os brinquedos da \Ncidade estão sempre cansados?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.03,0:03:19.21,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Que terrível! É terrível!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.21,0:03:21.55,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,D-De qualquer forma...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.55,0:03:25.18,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Fraland pode chegar à fábrica \Nde Smile por lá, certo?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.18,0:03:29.31,Main,Thunder Soldier,0,0,0,,Sim, há uma entrada em cada direção.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.31,0:03:32.56,Main,Thunder Soldier,0,0,0,,Mas é muito bem vigiada.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.56,0:03:35.17,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Do jeito que eu gosto.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.48,0:03:40.67,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Vou causar um grande alvoroço enquanto estiver lá.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.68,0:03:43.62,Main,Thunder Soldier,0,0,0,,P-Por que você faria isso?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.62,0:03:46.66,Flashbacks,Franky,0,0,0,,Isso vai facilitar as coisas para vocês, não é?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.66,0:03:47.52,Flashbacks,Thunder Soldier,0,0,0,,Você quer dizer que...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.52,0:03:52.91,Flashbacks,Franky,0,0,0,,Acabem com Sugar enquanto eu os distraio.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.54,0:04:04.92,Main,Pirate,0,0,0,,Quem é esse?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.82,0:04:06.99,Main,Pirate,0,0,0,,Uma tanga?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.99,0:04:08.83,Main,Pirate,0,0,0,,O que ele tem na cabeça?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.99,0:04:08.83,Secondary,Pirate,0,0,0,,O que ele tem na cabeça?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.33,0:04:11.53,Main,Pirate,0,0,0,,É uma arma?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.53,0:04:12.96,Main,Pirate,0,0,0,,Ou é um idiota?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.53,0:04:12.96,Secondary,Pirate,0,0,0,,Ou é um idiota?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.43,0:04:17.25,Main,Pirate,0,0,0,,Ei, olhem o queixo de garfo dele!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.83,0:04:23.93,Main,Pirate,0,0,0,,Não há dúvida! Esse é Franky, o Ciborgue, dos Piratas do Chapéu de Palha!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.22,0:04:35.46,Main,Woman,0,0,0,,Senhor! Você não deveria comer\N tomates assim!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.46,0:04:37.55,Main,Woman,0,0,0,,Você está sujando o rosto!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.97,0:04:50.27,Main,Woman,0,0,0,,Ele é tão...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.97,0:04:50.27,Secondary,Woman,0,0,0,,Ele é tão...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.84,0:04:54.88,Main,Woman,0,0,0,,...durão!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.84,0:04:54.88,Secondary,Woman,0,0,0,,...durão!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.88,0:04:58.10,Main,Pink,0,0,0,,{\an8}Não se aproximem tanto, garotas.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.46,0:05:02.25,OPLetreros,Caption,0,0,0,,{\pos(646,510)\fad(504,0)\bord2.0\fscx160\fscy160}FAMÍLIA DONQUIXOTE (OFICIAL DO EXÉRCITO DE ♦ DIAMANTE )
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.46,0:05:02.25,OPLetreros,Caption,0,0,0,,{\pos(646,720)\fad(504,0)\bord2.0\fscx160\fscy160}SENHOR PINK
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.29,0:05:02.25,Main,Pink,0,0,0,,{\an8}Vão brincar com alguém mais jovem.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.25,0:05:04.12,Main,Woman,0,0,0,,Não, Senhor!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.12,0:05:06.62,Main,Woman,0,0,0,,Não seja tão frio, Senhor!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.58,0:05:10.46,Main,Señor,0,0,0,,Garotas...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.82,0:05:13.83,Main,Señor,0,0,0,,Vocês não são do meu tipo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.84,0:05:16.70,Main,Woman,0,0,0,,Senhor!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.84,0:05:16.70,Secondary,Woman,0,0,0,,Senhor!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.70,0:05:18.72,Main,Woman,0,0,0,,Não me abandone, Senhor!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.72,0:05:20.67,Main,Woman,0,0,0,,Senhor!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.72,0:05:20.67,Secondary,Woman,0,0,0,,Senhor!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.67,0:05:22.91,Main,Woman,0,0,0,,Senhor!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.67,0:05:22.91,Secondary,Woman,0,0,0,,Senhor!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.54,0:05:27.31,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,E esse pervertido?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.31,0:05:29.07,Main,Pirate,0,0,0,,Olha quem fala!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.31,0:05:29.07,Secondary,Pirate,0,0,0,,Olha quem fala!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.07,0:05:32.10,Main,Pirate,0,0,0,,Chamando da entrada \Nleste da Casa dos Brinquedos!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.10,0:05:33.35,Main,Pirate,0,0,0,,Um deles está aqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.35,0:05:36.65,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Eles vão me deixar entrar.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.08,0:05:39.62,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Weapons Left!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.26,0:05:45.59,Main,Pirate,0,0,0,,Fogo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.86,0:05:48.52,Main,Pirate,0,0,0,,É um dos Piratas do Chapéu de Palha,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.52,0:05:50.43,Main,Pirate,0,0,0,,Franky, o Ciborgue!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.43,0:05:52.54,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Coup de...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.47,0:05:55.67,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,...Vent!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.74,0:06:11.68,Main,Doflamingo,0,0,0,,Olhe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.68,0:06:15.07,Main,Doflamingo,0,0,0,,Esses idiotas começaram a atacar.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.07,0:06:20.04,Main,Doflamingo,0,0,0,,Seu trabalho é ajudar os países\N aliados do Governo Mundial, certo?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.44,0:06:27.53,Main,Diamante,0,0,0,,Já começaram?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.81,0:06:45.44,Main,Sugar,0,0,0,,A Casa dos Brinquedos está sob ataque.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.25,0:06:48.57,Main,Trébol,0,0,0,,Não se preocupe!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.57,0:06:52.90,Main,Trébol,0,0,0,,Os Chapéu de Palha estão\N atrás da fábrica de Smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.90,0:06:56.09,Main,Trébol,0,0,0,,Mesmo que chegassem aqui...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.09,0:07:00.73,Main,Trébol,0,0,0,,Você pode transformar todos em brinquedos, certo?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.21,0:07:05.52,Main,Trébol,0,0,0,,Ninguém sabe!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.52,0:07:10.54,Main,Trébol,0,0,0,,Ninguém sabe nada sobre você!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.68,0:07:12.90,Main,Sugar,0,0,0,,É verdade.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.36,0:07:18.19,OPLetreros,Caption,0,0,0,,{\pos(660,545)\fad(506,0)\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170}PASSAGEM SUBTERRÂNEA
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.19,0:07:21.42,Main,Thunder Soldier,0,0,0,,Estamos quase no porto comercial.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.42,0:07:22.68,Main,Gnome,0,0,0,,Capitão!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.68,0:07:25.96,Main,Gnome,0,0,0,,Fraland começou seu ataque \Nna Casa dos Brinquedos!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.96,0:07:27.01,Main,Thunder Soldier,0,0,0,,Entendi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.01,0:07:31.63,Flashbacks,Franky,0,0,0,,{\fad(468,0)}Vou causar um grande alvoroço enquanto estiver lá.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.63,0:07:33.53,Main,Thunder Soldier,0,0,0,,Espero que ele esteja bem.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.53,0:07:37.14,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Não se preocupe, ele é um superciborgue.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.14,0:07:43.27,Main,Thunder Soldier,0,0,0,,Mas acabei de descobrir que há quatro oficiais da família protegendo a Casa dos Brinquedos.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.27,0:07:44.58,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,O-Oficiais?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.58,0:07:47.60,Main,Gnome,0,0,0,,De todos, tinha que ser logo o Exército do Diamante!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.60,0:07:49.75,Main,Gnome,0,0,0,,Eles são grandes lutadores.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.75,0:07:51.98,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Eles são muito fortes, hein?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.98,0:07:55.10,Main,Gnome,0,0,0,,Seu índice de vitória nos \Ntorneios de batalha é de 100%.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.10,0:07:57.29,Main,Gnome,0,0,0,,Eles são as grandes estrelas do coliseu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.29,0:07:59.41,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,100%?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.41,0:08:01.79,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Você está dizendo que eles nunca perderam?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.52,0:08:04.88,Main,Thunder Soldier,0,0,0,,Exato, em outras palavras,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.20,0:08:10.13,Main,Thunder Soldier,0,0,0,,ninguém sabe o alcance do poder deles.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.01,0:08:18.34,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Q-Quantos oficiais o inimigo tem, Leo?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.34,0:08:24.78,Main,Leo,0,0,0,,Dez oficiais comandam mais de \Ndois mil capangas por todo o país.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.78,0:08:28.89,Main,Leo,0,0,0,,Além disso, esses dez oficiais \Nrespondem a três chefes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.89,0:08:32.94,Main,Leo,0,0,0,,Cada um comanda seu próprio exército especializado.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.35,0:08:36.56,Main,Leo,0,0,0,,{\an8}Primeiro, o Exército de Trevo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.56,0:08:38.78,Main,Leo,0,0,0,,{\an8}Eles são a Equipe de Habilidades Especiais.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.09,0:08:39.01,OPLetreros,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fs45\fad(519,227)\pos(640,560)\bord2.0}EXÉRCITO DE TREVO (EQUIPE DE HABILIDADES ESPECIAIS)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.32,0:08:41.25,Main,Leo,0,0,0,,{\an8}Sugar!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.20,0:08:43.45,OPLetreros,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fs45\fad(491,491)\pos(640,580)\bord2.0}SUGAR
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.33,0:08:45.85,OP Normal2,Leo,0,0,0,,{\an8}Violet!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.70,0:08:47.96,Main,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fs45\fad(491,491)\pos(640,580)\bord2.0}VIOLET
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.28,0:08:50.70,Main,Leo,0,0,0,,{\an8}Giolla!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.20,0:08:52.49,OPLetreros,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fs45\fad(491,194)\pos(640,580)\bord2.0}GIOLLA
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.35,0:08:57.06,Main,Leo,0,0,0,,{\an8}Depois, há o Exército de Diamante.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.06,0:08:59.39,Main,Leo,0,0,0,,{\an8}Eles são os grandes lutadores.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.74,0:08:59.60,OPLetreros,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fs45\fad(500,227)\pos(640,560)\bord2.0}EXÉRCITO DE DIAMANTE (GRANDES LUTADORES)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.52,0:09:02.64,Main,Leo,0,0,0,,{\an8}Lao G!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.82,0:09:03.74,OPLetreros,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fs(45)\fad(491,200)\pos(640,570)\bord2.0}LAO G
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.36,0:09:06.63,Main,Leo,0,0,0,,{\an8}Machvise!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.89,0:09:07.58,OPLetreros,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fs(45)\fad(491,200)\pos(640,580)\bord2.0}MACHVISE
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.96,0:09:10.58,Main,Leo,0,0,0,,{\an8}Senhor Pink!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.86,0:09:11.81,OPLetreros,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fs(45)\fad(491,200)\pos(640,580)\bord2.0}SENHOR PINK
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.61,0:09:15.00,Main,Leo,0,0,0,,{\an8}Dellinger!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.00,0:09:15.95,OPLetreros,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fs(45)\fad(451,220)\pos(640,580)\bord2.0}DELLINGER
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.87,0:09:19.88,Main,Leo,0,0,0,,E, por último, o Exército de Pica.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.65,0:09:22.80,Main,Leo,0,0,0,,{\an8}Eles são a unidade de ataque!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.88,0:09:24.66,OPLetreros,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fs45\fad(520,227)\pos(650,560)\bord2.0}EXÉRCITO DE PICA (UNIDADE DE ATAQUE)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.32,0:09:27.58,Main,Leo,0,0,0,,{\an8}Gladius!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.80,0:09:28.76,OPLetreros,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fs(45)\fad(471,200)\pos(640,580)\bord2.0}GLADIUS
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.29,0:09:32.38,Main,Leo,0,0,0,,{\an8}Buffalo e Baby 5!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.89,0:09:33.73,OPLetreros,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fs45\fad(518,180)\pos(640,505)\bord2.0}BUFFALO E BABY 5
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.09,0:09:41.48,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Eu conheço Buffalo e Baby 5.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.23,0:09:45.78,Main,Leo,0,0,0,,{\an8}Também confirmamos mais dois que não estão no país agora.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.76,0:09:45.78,OPLetreros,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fs45\fad(168,0)\pos(640,560)\bord2.0}OFICIAL EM CHEFE - VERGO
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.36,0:09:49.50,Main,Leo,0,0,0,,{\an8}E a oficial Monet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.36,0:09:49.50,OPLetreros,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fs45\fad(218,0)\pos(640,565)\bord2.0}OFICIAL MONET
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.73,0:09:53.09,Thoughts,Usopp,0,0,0,,Então, não precisamos nos preocupar \Ncom os grandes lutadores.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.09,0:09:54.61,Thoughts,Usopp,0,0,0,,Vamos lá, Franky!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.61,0:09:57.01,Main,Leo,0,0,0,,Mas todos eles são muito fortes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.01,0:09:59.31,Thoughts,Usopp,0,0,0,,Não pode ser!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.07,0:10:09.22,Main,Leo,0,0,0,,Desculpe, Usoland!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.70,0:10:11.55,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,Obrigada.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.55,0:10:12.84,Main,Gancho,0,0,0,,Não é nada.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.84,0:10:14.85,Main,Leo,0,0,0,,Chegamos.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.85,0:10:18.53,Main,Leo,0,0,0,,Este é o mundo subterrâneo, \Nlar do porto comercial e da fábrica.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.37,0:10:22.87,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Tem muito barulho.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.91,0:10:27.67,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,São sons da superfície?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.67,0:10:30.71,Main,Pirate,0,0,0,,Ei, quem derrubou a carga?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.71,0:10:32.64,Main,Pirate,0,0,0,,Esse brinquedo não aguentou isso.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.64,0:10:34.60,Main,Toy,0,0,0,,D-Desculpe!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.60,0:10:38.25,Main,Toy,0,0,0,,Vou trabalhar mais duro, mas, \Npor favor, deixem-me ver minha família!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.25,0:10:41.99,Main,Pirate,0,0,0,,Idiota! Quem não der \Nconta vai direto para o lixo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.99,0:10:43.36,Main,Pirate,0,0,0,,Leve ele!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.36,0:10:46.30,Main,Toy,0,0,0,,E-Esperem! Ainda posso trabalhar!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.30,0:10:48.35,Main,Toy,0,0,0,,Socorro!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.30,0:10:50.66,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,Usopp...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.58,0:10:54.70,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Robin, você...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.23,0:10:58.51,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,Olhe.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.70,0:11:03.63,Main,Toy,0,0,0,,Ainda posso trabalhar!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.63,0:11:05.44,Main,Toy,0,0,0,,Socorro!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.44,0:11:08.76,Main,Pirate,0,0,0,,Se continuar exigindo tanto, \Nvocê vai ficar sem nada!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.76,0:11:11.44,Main,Pirate,0,0,0,,Desgraçado, não para de me irritar!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.44,0:11:13.69,Main,Pirate,0,0,0,,Se não tivesse o Joker-senpai \Ndo seu lado, eu juro que...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.62,0:11:25.60,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,O que é isso?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.60,0:11:28.65,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,É uma cidade portuária enorme!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.83,0:11:40.91,Main,Announcer,0,0,0,,Suleiman começa a atacar Rebecca!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.91,0:11:42.83,Main,Audience,0,0,0,,Vamos!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.83,0:11:44.59,Main,Audience,0,0,0,,Morra, Rebecca!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.59,0:11:48.34,Main,Audience,0,0,0,,Suleiman, corte sua cabeça!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.46,0:11:56.09,Main,Announcer,0,0,0,,Ele já foi um herói da Batalha Marinha de Dias e agora é um criminoso de guerra.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.09,0:12:00.06,Main,Announcer,0,0,0,,É um temido assassino do submundo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.21,0:12:07.44,Main,Announcer,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ele age como se fosse um fantasma!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.21,0:12:07.92,OPLetreros,Caption,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,480)\fad(525,525)\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170}CRIMINOSO DE GUERRA DE CLASSE A DA BATALHA MARINHA DE DIAS
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.21,0:12:07.92,OPLetreros,Caption,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,710)\fad(525,525)\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170}SULEIMAN, O DECAPITADOR
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.68,0:12:13.13,Main,Suleiman,0,0,0,,Vou dar tudo pelo meu país.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.13,0:12:14.72,Main,Suleiman,0,0,0,,Amo meu lar.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.71,0:12:18.85,Main,Suleiman,0,0,0,,E você?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.95,0:12:28.66,Main,Suleiman,0,0,0,,Deve ser difícil viver em um país cercada por pessoas que te abandonaram.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.96,0:12:32.43,Main,Rebecca,0,0,0,,Não importa o quão difícil seja.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.43,0:12:35.42,Main,Rebecca,0,0,0,,Não me importo quem me odeia.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.42,0:12:36.80,Main,Rebecca,0,0,0,,Eu...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.80,0:12:39.42,Main,Rebecca,0,0,0,,...quero viver com o Soldado-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.64,0:12:42.85,Main,Announcer,0,0,0,,Ela não quer morrer!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.85,0:12:49.18,Main,Announcer,0,0,0,,Incluindo a odiada Rebecca, restam \Ncerca de 30 combatentes no Bloco D.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.68,0:12:53.66,Main,Announcer,0,0,0,,Outro combatente foi derrotado!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.66,0:12:55.42,Main,Announcer,0,0,0,,Digo, um animal!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.17,0:12:58.40,Main,Announcer,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ele matou dezenas de pessoas...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.80,0:13:01.84,OPLetreros,Caption,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,480)\fad(525,525)\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170}MAIOR DA FROTA YONTA MARÍA {revisa, ryu xDD}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.80,0:13:01.84,OPLetreros,Caption,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,710)\fad(525,525)\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170}ORLUMBUS
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.40,0:13:00.01,Main,Announcer,0,0,0,,...e manchou o ringue de sangue.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.01,0:13:03.86,Main,Announcer,0,0,0,,Agyou, o leão gladiador, acabou...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.86,0:13:07.57,Main,Announcer,0,0,0,,...de cair para o chicote de Orlumbus.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.49,0:13:14.25,Main,Audience,0,0,0,,Que forte.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.25,0:13:15.58,Main,Audience,0,0,0,,Major!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.58,0:13:18.81,OPLetreros,Caption,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,545)\fad(525,0)\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170}CAVENDISH - PIRATA
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.86,0:13:22.11,OPLetreros,Caption,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,480)\fad(525,0)\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170}O DEMÔNIO DE FOGO
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.86,0:13:22.11,OPLetreros,Caption,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,710)\fad(525,0)\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170}DAMASK
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.26,0:13:18.81,Main,Announcer,0,0,0,,O vencedor será um dos favoritos?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.81,0:13:22.11,Main,Announcer,0,0,0,,Ou será alguém inesperado?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.11,0:13:25.92,Main,Announcer,0,0,0,,{\an8}Esta é a última batalha \Nantes da rodada final!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.12,0:13:25.92,OPLetreros,Caption,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,480)\fad(525,0)\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170}XAMÃ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.12,0:13:25.92,OPLetreros,Caption,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,710)\fad(525,0)\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170}MUMMY
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.92,0:13:28.42,Main,Announcer,0,0,0,,Quem tomará a cabeça...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.43,0:13:32.86,Main,Announcer,0,0,0,,...da neta do Rei Riku?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.42,0:13:37.40,Thoughts,Rebecca,0,0,0,,Soldado-san, onde você está agora?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.40,0:13:39.23,Thoughts,Rebecca,0,0,0,,Por favor, não morra.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.23,0:13:41.36,Thoughts,Rebecca,0,0,0,,Não peço mais nada.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.39,0:13:47.34,OPLetreros,Caption,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,545)\fad(525,0)\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170}BAIXO DRESSROSA - PORTO COMERCIAL SUBTERRÂNEO
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.79,0:14:02.59,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,O Soldado foi embora?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.59,0:14:03.83,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Ele não é o capitão?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.83,0:14:13.00,Main,Leo,0,0,0,,O capitão tem a importante missão de eliminar \NDoflamingo quando a operação SOP for bem-sucedida.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.00,0:14:17.46,Main,Leo,0,0,0,,Ele levou alguns Tontattas para o palácio.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.46,0:14:19.24,Main,Dwarf,0,0,0,,Boa sorte, capitão!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.24,0:14:21.57,Main,Dwarf,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.24,0:14:21.57,Secondary,Dwarf,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.12,0:14:25.81,Main,Leo,0,0,0,,Temos o herói Usoland do nosso lado.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.81,0:14:31.35,Main,Leo,0,0,0,,Usoland, por favor, lidere a operação \NSOP e nos ajude a derrotar Sugar.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.59,0:14:44.10,Thoughts,Usopp,0,0,0,,Essa não é a tarefa mais importante?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.89,0:14:50.86,Main,Leo,0,0,0,,Agora estamos aqui.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.42,0:14:55.64,OP_665_Signs,,0,500,80,,{\move(324,706,393,662,5,1474)\fs30}TRÉBOL
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.42,0:14:55.64,OP_665_Signs,,0,500,80,,{\move(634,724,631,662,5,1307)\fs30}SUGAR
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.11,0:14:55.64,OPLetreros,,0,400,80,,{\move(526,730,517,716,3,803)\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\fs20}TORRE DOS OFICIAIS
Dialogue: 1,0:14:51.69,0:14:55.14,Main,Leo,0,0,0,,{\an8}Todas as pontes são móveis.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.82,0:14:55.64,OP_665_Signs,,0,500,80,,{\move(236,96,311,160,5,2340)}ELEVADOR
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.52,0:14:55.64,OPLetreros,,0,500,80,,{\move(94,720,183,644,5,1507)\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\fs20}FÁBRICA
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.52,0:14:55.64,OPLetreros,,0,500,80,,{\move(1176,302,1129,284,5,1273)\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\fs20}PASSAGEM \NSUBTERRÂNEA
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.64,0:14:58.56,Main,Leo,0,0,0,,E aquele prédio ao longe...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.45,0:15:03.51,Main,Leo,0,0,0,,...que parece uma anêmona do mar...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.34,0:15:06.35,Main,Leo,0,0,0,,É a Torre dos Oficiais.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.35,0:15:08.62,Main,Leo,0,0,0,,É onde está Sugar.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.91,0:15:16.25,Main,Grunt,0,0,0,,Ei, por que estão perdendo tempo aqui?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.66,0:15:21.08,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Nos acharam! Acabou!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.08,0:15:24.20,Main,Grunt,0,0,0,,Desgraçados, de que navio são?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.20,0:15:28.10,Main,Grunt,0,0,0,,Não, espera, só estávamos passando por aqui.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.10,0:15:32.68,Main,Grunt,0,0,0,,Só os comerciantes podem descer dos navios.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.68,0:15:33.91,Main,Leo,0,0,0,,Inhel...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.91,0:15:34.65,Main,Inhel,0,0,0,,Sim.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.54,0:15:46.62,Main,Grunt,0,0,0,,As fadas estão aqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.62,0:15:48.23,Main,Grunt,0,0,0,,Elas nos tiraram tudo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.62,0:15:48.23,Secondary,Grunt,0,0,0,,Elas nos tiraram tudo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.23,0:15:50.81,Main,Leo & Inhel,0,0,0,,Tonttata Combat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.23,0:15:50.81,NDTBoard,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\1a&H80&\fad(300,0)\t(0,300,\fscx570)\move(133,65,133,-57,1920,2420)}Mola
Dialogue: 1,0:15:48.23,0:15:50.81,NDTSkull,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\fad(300,0)\move(60,69,60,-53,1920,2420)}Shi
Dialogue: 2,0:15:48.23,0:15:50.81,NDTHat,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\fad(300,0)\move(58,72,58,-50,1920,2420)}Chibukai
Dialogue: 3,0:15:48.23,0:15:50.81,NDTHat2,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\fad(300,0)\move(58,72,58,-50,1920,2420)}Fansub!
Dialogue: 4,0:15:48.23,0:15:50.81,NDTText,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\alpha&HFF&\t(300,600,\alpha&H00&)\move(650,35,650,-81,1920,2420)}Estilo de combate Tontatta.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.81,0:15:52.90,Main,Leo & Inhel,0,0,0,,Shippo Hammer!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.81,0:15:52.90,Secondary,Leo & Inhel,0,0,0,,Shippo Hammer!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.77,0:16:00.37,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,E-Eles foram enterrados no chão!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.93,0:16:03.68,Main,Cotton,0,0,0,,Vistam isso, Usoland, Robiland.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.68,0:16:07.69,Main,Flapper,0,0,0,,Mas que inteligente...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.69,0:16:10.80,Main,Flapper,0,0,0,,Ele fingiu estar assustado para \Ndistrair o inimigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.37,0:16:17.63,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,A propósito, todos são tão fortes assim?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.63,0:16:19.26,Main,Flapper,0,0,0,,Sim, todos somos.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.26,0:16:23.87,Main,Leo,0,0,0,,Mas o clã de Noland é capaz \Nde matar reis marinhos.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.87,0:16:25.26,Main,Leo,0,0,0,,Não somos rivais para eles...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.21,0:16:31.09,Thoughts,Usopp,0,0,0,,Que tipo de monstro vocês acham que eu sou?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.80,0:16:38.94,Thoughts,Usopp,0,0,0,,Mas talvez eu possa vencer sem lutar.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.94,0:16:43.05,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Certo, pessoal, eu, Usoland, \Nvou assumir o comando!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.05,0:16:44.92,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Nossa oponente é uma garota!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.92,0:16:48.19,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Vamos em grupo para assustá-la!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.19,0:16:49.59,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Sigam-me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.59,0:16:51.22,Main,Dwarves,0,0,0,,Sim, senhor!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.59,0:16:51.22,Secondary,Dwarves,0,0,0,,Sim, senhor!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.22,0:16:54.26,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Ah... não... esperem...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.26,0:16:56.26,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Vão na frente!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.26,0:16:59.36,Main,Dwarves,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.26,0:16:59.36,Secondary,Dwarves,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.36,0:17:02.17,Main,Leo,0,0,0,,Para a Torre dos Oficiais!
